dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.swcomponenttemplate.portinterface

Interface ITextTableMapping

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface ITextTableMapping
extends IEntity
    ITextTableMapping: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Defines the mapping of two DataPrototypes typed by AutosarDataTypes that refer to CompuMethods of category TEXTTABLE, SCALE_LINEAR_AND_TEXTTABLE or BITFIELD_TEXTTABLE.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
